{"tid":51320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最無知國家排行　中國No.2台灣No.3","createTime":"2016-12-23T06:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T15:00:19.000Z","uid":491,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d84115d85d350361d70b7c6271c15f4f66da8fc","tid":51320,"uid":491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:29:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161223/1019132/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20161223%2F1019132%2F&d=PyvhatFNHvf0VQZCNupr9ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f67b5cb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161223/1019132/</a><br />\n<br />\n識睇一定睇佢fb page入面d台仔係呢個新聞既留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798130264e875bbfe4b0514a334c5f535f6887bd","tid":51320,"uid":11376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:35:38.000Z","msg":"最無知國家 有台灣<br />\n又有玻璃心要碎"},{"pid":"c199fa2d216572de68a3af5ee3b897867c8cebe9","tid":51320,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 台狗同支那狗又要吠"},{"pid":"6e62880b8c4dc2e2834d47ecc7a769f3ed9ca5c1","tid":51320,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T07:40:32.000Z","msg":"英國一間調查機構，就四十個國家及地區的民眾，對社會真實情況的認知，展開調查，並制訂「全球無知排名」，排首位的是印度，反映民眾的認知，嚴重脫離現實，其次是中國大陸及台灣。香港排名十七，稍低於菲律賓。調查在九至十一月進行，訪問了四十個國家及地區，超過二萬七千人。受訪者需要回答一系列社會問題，包括住屋、醫療保健及伊斯蘭教徒比例，然後比較真實數字，按照答錯程度，制訂「無知排名」。<span style=\"color: red;\">在人口數字方面，香港受訪者表現是全球最差，一般回答香港有八百萬人口。而最掌握社會實況的國家，分別是荷蘭、英國及南韓。</span><br />\n<br />\nFrom 881903<br />\n<br />\n港豬有咩資格笑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faad9738e70437e6801bd1797d5bf87de8939dd","tid":51320,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}